<plot>When you look like America's enemy, is the Dream worth the price? A Dream in Doubt is an immigrant story in a world in which patriotism has morphed into murder. When Rana Singh Sodhi's brother is killed in America's first post-9/11 revenge murder, he begins a journey to reclaim his American dream and fight the hate that continues to threaten his community.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?009897</url></doc>
